.TH "devm_ioremap" 9 "devm_ioremap" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
devm_ioremap \- Managed ioremap()
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void __iomem *" devm_ioremap
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "resource_size_t offset "  ","
.BI "resource_size_t size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Generic device to remap IO address for
.IP "offset" 12
Resource address to map
.IP "size" 12
Size of map
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Managed \fBioremap\fP.  Map is automatically unmapped on driver detach.
